name: Obtain Federal EIN for Interface & Co
notes: Must use Form SS-4 by fax due to IRS system issues. Sub-tasks: Complete Form SS-4, fax to 855-641-6935, follow up on processing

name: File First Statement of Information with CA Secretary of State for Interface & Co
notes: Due within 90 days of formation. Sub-tasks: Gather member info, file online at bizfileonline.sos.ca.gov, pay $20 fee

name: Draft Operating Agreement for Interface & Co
notes: Sub-tasks: Research templates, customize for your needs, review with attorney if needed, execute and store

name: Pay California LLC $800 Franchise Tax for Interface & Co
notes: Annual requirement. Sub-tasks: Complete Form FTB 3522, submit payment online or by mail

name: File Form 568 LLC Tax Return for Interface & Co
notes: Due April 15 with automatic extension to Nov 15. Required even for disregarded entities. Sub-tasks: Make disregarded entity election on form, gather financial records, complete return, file electronically

name: Pay Additional LLC Fee for Interface & Co (if gross receipts > $250,000)
notes: Only if applicable. Sub-tasks: Calculate annual gross receipts, determine fee tier, submit payment if required

name: Include Interface & Co Income on Joint Tax Return
notes: Federal requirement. Sub-tasks: Elect disregarded entity treatment, gather business records, complete Schedule C, file with joint 1040

name: Obtain Business Insurance for Interface & Co
notes: Before business operations ramp up. Sub-tasks: Research general liability options, get quotes from 3+ insurers, select policy, purchase coverage

name: File Biennial Statement of Information for Interface & Co (every 2 years)
notes: 2 years after first filing. Sub-tasks: Update member information, file online, pay $20 fee

name: Check ImmiAccount and Review Currently Uploaded Documents for Baby's Citizenship
notes: Application pending since April 30th. Sub-tasks: Login to ImmiAccount, check what's already uploaded, identify gaps from government checklist

name: Submit Missing Documents for Baby's Australian Citizenship Application
notes: 4+ month delay already! Required docs: Your citizenship evidence, foreign citizenship proof, birth certificate, Form 1195 (all pages), marriage certificate, government ID for both parents, residential addresses

name: Apply for Australian ETA for Baby (October Trip)
notes: For October 8th travel. Sub-tasks: Download Australian ETA app, enter US passport details, pay AUD $20, receive instant approval

name: Get Australian Passport Photos at Leetone Photo Center
notes: 35mm x 45mm format. Location: 480 Davis Court, SF Financial District. Needed for eventual passport application

name: Determine NSW Name Change Registration Requirements
notes: Check if marriage certificate suffices or if formal name change required for document consistency

name: Register Name Change with NSW BDM (if required)
notes: Only if needed. Online application, $195 AUD fee, 10+ business days processing

name: Apply for Australian Passport with Priority Processing
notes: For December 15th travel. Can only apply after citizenship approval. Requires guarantor (Australian citizen who's known baby since birth)

name: Arrange Guarantor for Australian Passport Application
notes: Must be Australian citizen who has known baby since birth. Contact Australian friends/family, explain requirements
